channel.title: Looking for a coder/developer for Insanityx Source
channel.description: Hello me and a buddy havd just opened up a server today and we are looking for a coder/developer that has experience in things like adding a GE, vote4cash, donation system, coding aspects of certain skills like adding level requirements for certain slayer monsters, and minor bugs. The source is Insanityx please let me know if you would like to join the team!
